  "instructions": [
    "Peel and mash the bananas in a bowl.",
    "Heat 2 tbsp coconut oil in a skillet over medium heat.",
    "Fry the banana slices until golden, about 2 minutes per side.",
    "Remove the fried bananas and set aside to cool slightly.",
    "In a blender, combine coconut milk, garlic, maple syrup, soy sauce, aquafaba, cashew cream, and sea salt.",
    "Blend until the mixture is smooth and aerated.",
    "Fold in the fried banana slices gently into the mousse mixture.",
    "Serve the mousse chilled in individual cups for a velvety finish."
  ],
